cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.HC 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on dialogue analysis and proposes a new dataset for investigating shared dialogue history. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is also likely as the dataset is visually grounded and involves referring to images. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper proposes a baseline model for reference resolution. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper discusses the need for more sophisticated models of common ground in dialogue interaction. 
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is also relevant as the paper describes a collaborative game used to collect the dataset and discusses the implications for dialogue interaction.
